    "One such activity is the Ponzi scheme, where investors are promised high returns but the returns are paid from the capital invested by new investors rather than from actual profits.",
    "The decentralied nature of the blockchain can make it difficult for authorities to detect and shut down these schemes.",
    "Hacking attacks and data breaches are also concerns in the blockchain space.",
    "In 2019, the cryptocurrency exchange Binance suffered a hack that resulted in the loss of over $40 million worth of Bitcoin.",
    "The hack was made possible due to a vulnerability in the exchange's security measures (DuPont 2019)."
